  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The hotel offers a varied continental buffet breakfast served between 7.30 - 10.30am.</p>
<p>Dinner is served at the L'Aiglon restaurant between 7-9:30pm and consists of a three course evening meal including a <span>starter, main course and dessert. </span></p>
<p>There is also the possibility to sample regional fondue or raclette for an additional supplement (payable locally). </p>
<p>Christmas and New Year gala dinners included.</p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
